            "description": "Non-planar two-loop integral family F (Bonciani et al. labeling A-G) for Higgs+jet production $gg \\to gH$ with full heavy-quark mass dependence. 7 propagators (3 massless, 4 massive with quark mass $m$), 2 ISPs. 73 master integrals: 65 polylogarithmic + 8 elliptic in sectors 126/127. Canonical DE for polylog sectors with 76-letter alphabet; generalized series expansion for elliptic sectors. Three massless external legs ($p_1,p_2,p_3$) and one massive leg $p_4$ with $p_4^2 = m_H^2 = s+t+u$.",
